  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your own shoe store and build it into a successful business! Stock your shelves with the latest shoes, hire employees to help you, and design your store the way you want. Manage your inventory, keep your customers happy, and expand your store to grow your business. Can you create the ultimate shoe store? Start your journey now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the Features of the Game:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Order and Stock Inventory:</strong> Choose shoes to stock up your store and organize them on shelves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/49c81c723802a520d20229b017c7fab3.poster.avif?t=1765284135\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/49c81c723802a520d20229b017c7fab3.webm?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/49c81c723802a520d20229b017c7fab3.mp4?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize Your Store:</strong> Change your store’s name, paint walls, floors, and shelves, then choose your favorite decorations to create a space that's uniquely yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/a1d9c4394132f646675689d1294490f9.poster.avif?t=1765284135\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/a1d9c4394132f646675689d1294490f9.webm?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/a1d9c4394132f646675689d1294490f9.mp4?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/795091b606d8e937644ec0d4075348d4.poster.avif?t=1765284135\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/795091b606d8e937644ec0d4075348d4.webm?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/795091b606d8e937644ec0d4075348d4.mp4?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/5d7cddc362395daca639d5d194c0a972.poster.avif?t=1765284135\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/5d7cddc362395daca639d5d194c0a972.webm?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/5d7cddc362395daca639d5d194c0a972.mp4?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expand Your Business:</strong> Hiring employees for tasks such as restocking shelves, organizing inventory, and cashier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/9ccb832afe25594a886c8cfa17ff8d47.poster.avif?t=1765284135\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/9ccb832afe25594a886c8cfa17ff8d47.webm?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/9ccb832afe25594a886c8cfa17ff8d47.mp4?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your own shoe store and build it into a successful business! Stock your shelves with the latest shoes, hire employees to help you, and design your store the way you want. Manage your inventory, keep your customers happy, and expand your store to grow your business. Can you create the ultimate shoe store? Start your journey now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the Features of the Game:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Order and Stock Inventory:</strong> Choose shoes to stock up your store and organize them on shelves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/49c81c723802a520d20229b017c7fab3.poster.avif?t=1765284135\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/49c81c723802a520d20229b017c7fab3.webm?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/49c81c723802a520d20229b017c7fab3.mp4?t=1765284135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize Your Store:</strong> Change your store’s name, paint walls, floors, and shelves, then choose your favorite decorations to create a space that's uniquely yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/a1d9c4394132f646675689d1294490f9.poster.avif?t=1765284135\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319250/extras/a1d9c4394132f646675689d1294490f9.webm?t=1765284135\" type=\